  children massasoit had five children : " moanam " , or wamsutta , who was born sometime between 1621 and 1624 ; pometecomet , metacomet , or metacom ; a third son , sonkanuchoo ; and two daughters , one named amie and one whose name is unrecorded .

colonial america : " king philip " , who led bloody indian war , was son of massasoit who , in 1621 , met these people in friendship

the pilgrims